<item>
            <title>[HBASE-840] More options on the row query in REST interface</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-840</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The prior implementation only supports the exact column name(col_family:label), but we need more such as get a col family, query the version. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
